  "text": "However, it was significantly reduced on the 2nd day and became zero on the 6th day in case of the treatment groups. But the control group again felt pain on the 5th day which reduced to zero on the 7th day. Our findings are similar to those of [CITATION_1] who enunciated that 28% of participants felt pain in the first night and that gradually decreased within 5 days [CITATION_2] .",
